Resolved,
That the Orders made by the Secretary of State under the Sunday Entertainments Act, 1932, for extending Section one of that Act to the under mentioned areas, namely:



(1)the Rural District of Barnet;

(2)the rural District of Erpingham (Parish of Holt);
copies of which were presented to this House on 27th May, be approved." — [Mr. Herbert Morrison.]
